    <item>
      <title>蓬勃发展的印度一级市场吸引高价股票的资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/booming-india-primary-market-lures-funds-away-from-pricey-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度新股发行的持续热潮引起了全球基金的兴趣，他们似乎因为印度的二级市场估值过高而避开了印度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/booming-india-primary-market-lures-funds-away-from-pricey-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因中国企业盈利令人失望而下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三亚洲股市下跌，因中国企业盈利疲软引发人们对其经济疲软的新担忧。交易员也在等待英伟达公司的业绩，以寻找人工智能相关股票增长势头的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 22:28:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔信号带来的提振作用消退，比特币跌至一周低点</title>
